          <span class="text-white font-bold">Water</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">stay hydrated</span>
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Snacks</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">light energy</span>
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Pen</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">for scoring</span>
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Arrive early</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">15-30 min</span>
        </span>
      </div>

      <p>Arrive early enough to check your pairings, find your table, and settle in. Rushing creates anxiety that affects your first game. Most venues provide tiles, boards, and clocks — but confirm beforehand.</p>

